9780233.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742710-intel-should-have-kept-gelsinger-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 01:05:41"}, {"id": "4742000", "title": "NewLake Capital's Inherent Undervaluation Offers Opportunistic Investors With Rich Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A US Dollar symbol made of wood with leaves growing from it.\" data-id=\"1455774438\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>NLCP Is Inherently Undervalued - Offering Opportunistic Investors With The Dual Pronged Returns</strong></h2> <p>We previously covered <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4715636-newlake-capital-lock-in-yields-cannabis-federal-rescheduling-near\">NewLake Capital Partners</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NLCP\" title=\"NewLake Capital Partners, Inc.\">OTCQX:NLCP</a>) in August 2024, discussing its outperformance through the robust FQ2'24 performance metrics as its tenants' profitability continued to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742000-newlake-capitals-inherent-undervaluation-offers-opportunistic-investors-with-rich-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 00:00:00"}, {"id": "4742706", "title": "Hormel: Q4 Earnings Confirm It's Better To Own The Retailer Than The Brand (Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Full shopping cart in supermarket aisle\" data-id=\"482142025\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/4821420